OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome rain in
OL,6,Fthe northwest this evening otherwise a
OL,7,Fmainly dry end to the day. Then the
OL,8,Frest of the night will be cloudy with
OL,9,Fsome patchy light rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMainly dry with some warm
OL,12,Fsunshine breaking through, but the
OL,13,Fnorthwest will be cloudy with a little
OL,14,Frain, especially later on.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry on Friday, patchy light rain in
OL,18,Fthe west. Widespread rain will spread
OL,19,Fsoutheast on Saturday followed by a
OL,20,Ffew showers. Mainly dry with bright
OL,21,Fspells on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
